org.apache.ambari.server.orm.dao

Class AlertSummaryDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.orm.dao.AlertSummaryDTO
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HostAlertSummaryDTO

    public class AlertSummaryDTO
extends Object
    Used to return alert summary data out of the database. Alerts that are in maintenance mode will be reported as such instead of their actual values.
